00:01:05.973 --> 00:01:10.006
which prohibits state governments
from abusing its citizens,

00:01:10.030 --> 00:01:12.576
does not require state
governments to intervene

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:15.335
when private parties abuse its citizens.

00:01:16.001 --> 00:01:17.779
So what does that mean in real life?

00:01:18.319 --> 00:01:21.583
